What you need to know:  Machoka noted that Nation Media Group decided to venture into sports production and the purchase of, among other properties, the WRC Safari Rally’s broadcast rights owing to the rich tradition of these properties.“Last year’s Safari Rally is said to have injected Sh6.7 billion into the Kenyan economy and we are also looking at the eyeballs with the global audience of about 80 million for the Safari Rally alone and a cumulative 800 million for the entire World Rally Championship circuit, it’s quite encouraging,” Machoka said.